item.title: Yuliya Rai - our Ukrainian singer appeared on X Factor!!!!!!
item.description: Click on the link below to watch our Yuliya performing on X FACTOR on Channel 7 (There might be some advertising shown first). Well done Yuliya!!!!! http://au.tv.yahoo.com/x-factor/video/-/watch/21707451/yuliya-rai/ Yuliya has performed a number of times at the Ukrainian Community Centre in Brisbane. In fact Yuliya just performed at the Ukrainian Independence day concert in Brisbane on 22 August 2010. We already know she is great. Lets hope the judges see her at her best.
